	(text "This section of the schematic covers everything \nthat happens at 3.3VDC or 5VDC, including the \nmicrocontroller, peripherals, and some of the \nsimple circuits needed to support the operation \n\nPower for this section is provided by a sealed \nswitching transformer soldered onto the board. "
